        <name>VersionId</name>
        <qualifiedname>helios::engine::common::types::VersionId</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Version number for detecting stale entity references. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Each entity slot in an EntityPool has an associated version that is incremented when the entity is removed. EntityHandles store both the EntityId and <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1common_1_1types_1aca719bfaa89c70b354105a2d914e83b7" kindref="member">VersionId</ref>, allowing the pool to detect when a handle refers to a recycled slot.</para>
<para>A valid version starts at 1 (uninitialized handles have version 0).</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>EntityHandle </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>EntityId </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>EntityPool </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
